overview: For over thirty-five years, the lawyers at the Cochran Firm Wisconsin, formerly the Techmeier Law Firm,have worked aggressively and tirelessly to get our clients the compensation they deserve. As one of Wisconsin’s most recognized personal injury law firms, we have focused on providing victims and their families the legal guidance and representation they need during difficult times. Call 1-800-INJURED for a free case evaluation. There is no fee unless you win.
